<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-Right:4pt;width:6%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">10</a></p></td>
<td valign="middle"  style="width:94%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:16pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#5A2D82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2019 Proxy Statement</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;ITEM 1. Election of Directors&#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU16"></a><a name="DIRECTOR_NOMINEES_FOR_ELECTION_AT_ANNUAL"></a><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="DIRECTOR_NOMINEES_FOR_ELECTION_AT_ANNUAL"></a>Director Nominees for Elect</font><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">ion at the Annual Meeting </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Individual Nominees&#8217; Experience, Qualifications, Attributes and Skills </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The Board believes that each director nominee for election at the 2019 Annual Meeting is highly qualified. All 13 director nominees satisfy the Guidelines&#8217; criteria and possess the personal attributes essential for the proper and effective functioning of the Board. The director nominees&#8217; biographies describe the specific qualifications that the Governance Committee relied upon when it recommended the individual director nominees for election and led the Board to nominate him or her for election. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The biographies also include information about current and past (covering the last five years) directorships at companies publicly listed in the United States and registered investment companies, as required by the proxy disclosure rules. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">A particular director nominee may have experience and qualifications in addition to those described in the biographies below, including service on the boards of various private companies, companies listed outside of the United States and charitable, educational and cultural institutions. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;"><a name="_Hlk530590195"></a>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU17"></a><font style="font-size:6pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</font></p>

<td valign="top"  style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:1pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:1pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>

<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;<img src="gycirsmwh4vw000054.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:87px;height:128px;"><font style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times New Roman;"></font></p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">LEWIS W.K. BOOTH</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Former Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Ford Motor Company</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since: <font style="font-weight:normal;">October 2012</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Age:<font style="font-weight:normal;"> 70</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Independent</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committees:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Finance</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Human Resources and Compensation</font></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249090"></a>Mr.&#160;Booth served as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of Ford Motor Company (&#8220;Ford&#8221;), a global automobile manufacturer, from November 2008 until his retirement in April 2012. He was Executive Vice President of Ford of Europe, Volvo Car Corporation and Ford Export Operations and Global Growth Initiatives, and Executive Vice President of Ford&#8217;s Premier Automotive Group from October 2005 to October 2008. Prior to that, Mr.&#160;Booth held various executive leadership positions with Ford, including Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Ford of Europe, President of Mazda Motor Corporation and President of Ford Asia Pacific and Africa Operations. He worked for Ford in various positions from 1978 to 2012.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Mr.&#160;Booth was appointed Commander of the Order of the British Empire in June 2012 for his services to the United Kingdom&#8217;s automotive and manufacturing industries.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;During his career at Ford, Mr.&#160;Booth gained global business experience. He led operations in Africa, Asia and Europe. In these and other roles, he successfully implemented major growth initiatives, business restructuring and cost management and was involved in strategy, product development, marketing and operations.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Booth held a variety of positions on Ford&#8217;s Finance staff. As Ford&#8217;s Chief Financial Officer during the 2008 financial crisis, Mr.&#160;Booth led a restructuring of Ford&#8217;s balance sheet and a return to growth and profitability.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Booth is a Chartered Management Accountant.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Booth has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. He is a director&#160;of Rolls-Royce Holdings plc and a former director of Gentherm Incorporated.</font><font style="font-size:4pt;color:#000000;">&#160;</font></p></td>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></div>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU18"></a>&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:12pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000055.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:87px;height:127px;"></p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">CHARLES E. BUNCH</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Retired Executive Chairman, PPG Industries, Inc.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since: <font style="font-weight:normal;">September 2016</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Age:<font style="font-weight:normal;"> 69</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Independent</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committees:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Governance, Membership and Public&#160;Affairs</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:14.4pt;;text-indent:-8.65pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Human Resources and Compensation</font></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249114"></a>Mr.&#160;Bunch served as Executive Chairman of PPG Industries, Inc. (&#8220;PPG&#8221;), a manufacturer and distributor of a broad range of coatings, specialty materials and glass products, from September 2015 until his retirement in August 2016. He served as Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer from July 2005 until August 2015; President and Chief Executive Officer from March 2005 until July 2005; President and Chief Operating Officer from July 2002 to March 2005; Executive Vice President, Coatings from 2000 to 2002 and Senior Vice President, Strategic Planning and Corporate Services from 1997 to 2000. He joined PPG in 1979 and held various positions in finance and planning, marketing and general management in the United States and Europe.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:-0.1pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Mr. Bunch is a former a director and chairman of the Federal Reserve Bank of Cleveland. He was appointed chairman of the Pittsburgh office of the Federal Reserve Bank of Cleveland from 2001 to 2002; deputy chairman of the Cleveland office from 2003 to 2005; and chairman of the Cleveland office in 2006.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:-0.1pt;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;<font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">During his 37-year career at PPG, Mr.&#160;Bunch gained valuable experience in executive leadership, operations management, cost management, risk management and strategic planning.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;<font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Under Mr.&#160;Bunch&#8217;s leadership, PPG accelerated its business transformation, becoming the world&#8217;s leading paints and coatings company through strategic actions that focused its business portfolio and expanded and strengthened its international presence. During his tenure as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, PPG made more than 30 acquisitions and delivered strong growth and record financial performance.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;<font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Through his service at the Federal Reserve Bank of Cleveland, including as its Chairman, Mr.&#160;Bunch gained a deep understanding of the U.S. economy and corporate finance.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;<font style="font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">&#160;</font><font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Mr.&#160;Bunch has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. He is a director of Marathon Petroleum Corporation, ConocoPhilips and The PNC Financial Services Group, Inc. and a former director of H.J. Heinz Company and PPG.</font></p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>

<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;ITEM 1. Election of Directors&#160;&#160;</font></p>

<tr style="height:1pt;">
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU19"></a><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000056.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:88px;height:130px;"><font style="font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"></font></p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">DEBRA A. CREW</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Former President and Chief Executive Officer, Reynolds American Inc., British American Tobacco p.l.c.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since: <font style="font-weight:normal;">March 2018</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Age:<font style="font-weight:normal;"> 48</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Independent</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committees: </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Audit</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Finance</font></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249179"></a>&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Ms.&#160;Crew has served as a senior advisor for Cerberus Operations and Advisory Company, a capital management company, since September 2018. She previously served as Director, President and Chief Executive Officer of Reynolds American Inc. (&#8220;Reynolds American&#8221;), a holding company for U.S. tobacco companies, from January 2017 through December 2017, including from July 2017 when Reynolds American was acquired by British American Tobacco p.l.c.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Prior to that, she served as President and Chief Commercial Officer of R. J. Reynolds Tobacco Co. (&#8220;RJR&#8221;), a subsidiary of Reynolds American and a tobacco company, from October 2014 to October 2015 and as President and Chief Operating Officer of RJR from October 2015 to December 2016.<font style="font-size:6pt;"> </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Ms.&#160;Crew previously served in a variety of executive roles at PepsiCo, Inc. (&#8220;PepsiCo&#8221;), a global snack and beverage company, including President and General Manager, PepsiCo North America Nutrition from August 2014 to September 2014, President, PepsiCo Americas Beverages from October 2012 through August 2014 and President, Western European Region of PepsiCo Europe from April 2010 through October 2012.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Prior to that, Ms.&#160;Crew held positions of increasing responsibility at Kraft Foods, Nestl&#233; S.A. (&#8220;Nestl&#233;&#8221;) and Mars, Incorporated (&#8220;Mars&#8221;), all global food companies, from 1997 to 2010. Ms.&#160;Crew served as a captain in the U.S. Army in military intelligence from 1993 to 1997.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Ms.&#160;Crew possesses invaluable perspective and experience as former President and Chief Executive Officer of Reynolds American.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Ms.&#160;Crew has significant knowledge of the food and beverage industry and consumer products generally attained through her service in various positions of increasing responsibility, including key executive roles, at Kraft Foods, Nestl&#233; and PepsiCo.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Ms.&#160;Crew</font><font style="color:#5A2D82;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;">has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. She is a director of Newell Brands Inc. and </font><font style="color:#000000;">Stanley Black&#160;&amp; Decker, Inc. She is a former</font><font style="color:#000000;"> director of </font><font style="color:#000000;">Reynolds American.</font></p></td>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Former Vice Chairman and Chief Operating Officer, Colgate-Palmolive Company</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since: <font style="font-weight:normal;">November 2007</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committees:</p>

<p style="margin-bottom:6pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Human Resources and Compensation (Chair)</font></p></td>

<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>

<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249205"></a>Ms.&#160;Juliber served as Vice Chairman of the Colgate-Palmolive Company (&#8220;Colgate-Palmolive&#8221;), a global consumer products company, from 2004 until her retirement in April 2005. She served as Colgate-Palmolive&#8217;s Chief Operating Officer from 2000 to 2004, Executive Vice President&#160;&#8211;&#160;North America and Europe from 1997 until 2000, President of Colgate North America from 1994 to 1997 and Chief Technology Officer from 1991 until 1994.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Prior to joining Colgate-Palmolive, Ms.&#160;Juliber spent 15 years at Mondel&#275;z International&#8217;s predecessor, General Foods Corporation, in a variety of key marketing and general management positions.&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Ms.&#160;Juliber brings a global perspective and many years of experience in the food and consumer products industries.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;As Vice Chairman and Chief Operating Officer of Colgate-Palmolive, she led Colgate-Palmolive&#8217;s growth functions, including global marketing and business development, research and development, supply chain operations and investor relations.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Ms. Juliber is credited with leading the resurgence of Colgate-Palmolive&#8217;s Colgate North America business, which was marked by market share increases, highly successful new products and increased profitability.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:4pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Ms.&#160;Juliber also has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. Ms.&#160;Juliber is a director of DowDuPont Inc. (successor of E.I. du Pont de Nemours and Company). She is a former director of Goldman Sachs Group, Inc.</font></p></td>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU21"></a><font style="font-size:6pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</font></p>

<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000059.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:88px;height:130px;"></p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">MARK D. KETCHUM</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Former President and Chief Executive Officer, Newell Rubbermaid Inc<font style="font-size:9pt;">.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since: <font style="font-weight:normal;">April 2007</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Age:<font style="font-weight:normal;"> 69</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Independent</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committee:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Human Resources and Compensation </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:8.65pt;;text-indent:-8.65pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249238"></a>&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Mr. Ketchum served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Newell Rubbermaid Inc. (&#8220;Newell Rubbermaid&#8221;), a global marketer of consumer and commercial products, from October 2005 until his retirement in June 2011. He was a member of Newell Rubbermaid&#8217;s board of directors from November 2004 to May 2012.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">From 1971 to 2004, Mr.&#160;Ketchum served in a variety of roles at The Procter&#160;&amp; Gamble Company (&#8220;P&amp;G&#8221;), a global marketer of consumer products. Those roles included President, Global Baby and Family Care from 1999 to 2004, President&#160;&#8211;&#160;North American Paper Sector from 1996 to 1999, and Vice President and General Manager&#160;&#8211;&#160;Tissue/Towel from 1990 to 1996. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:4pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;For over four decades, Mr.&#160;Ketchum held key executive roles at global consumer products companies with responsibility for operations, brand management, marketing and general management.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;While serving as Newell Rubbermaid&#8217;s President and Chief Executive Officer, he successfully transformed Newell Rubbermaid&#8217;s portfolio, gross margin structure and business model during difficult economic times.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;During his distinguished 33-year career at P&amp;G, among other accomplishments, he was credited with repositioning key brands and for driving their notable profit and share growth and leading the turnaround of a major global brand.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Ketchum has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. He is a former director of Newell Rubbermaid and previously served as Lead Director for the Mondel&#275;z International Board from its inception through 2018.</font><font style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times New Roman;color:#000000;"> </font></p></td>

<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249273"></a>Mr.&#160;May has served as President and a Founding Partner of Trian Fund Management, L.P. (&#8220;Trian&#8221;), an investment management firm, since November 2005. He also served as President and Chief Operating Officer and a director of Triarc Companies, Inc. (now known as The Wendy&#8217;s Company), a holding company for various consumer and industrial businesses, from April 1993 to June 2007, and has served as its non-Executive Vice Chairman since June 2007.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Prior to that, Mr.&#160;May served as President and Chief Operating Officer of Trian Group, Limited Partnership, which provided investment banking and management services to entities controlled by Mr.&#160;May and Nelson Peltz, from January 1989 to April 1993 and as President and Chief Operating Officer of Triangle Industries, Inc., a manufacturer of packaging products, from 1983 to December 1988.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;May has extensive investment, financial and leadership experience as President and a Founding Partner of Trian, working with management teams and boards of directors, as well as acquiring, investing in and building companies. He has a deep understanding of the capital markets. He also has strong relationships with institutional investors and within the investment banking/capital markets.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;May has considerable experience with large, complex food service organizations such as The Wendy&#8217;s Company, with a focus on operational efficiency and effectiveness.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;May has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. He is a director of The Wendy&#8217;s Company. He is a former director of Tiffany&#160;&amp; Co. from 2008 to 2017.</font></p></td>
</tr>

Election of Directors&#160;&#160;</font></p>

<div style="width:100%;">
<div style="float:left;width:49%;">

<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:15%;">

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:8.65pt;;text-indent:-8.65pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:14.4pt;;text-indent:-8.65pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">JORGE S. MESQUITA</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:7.25pt;;text-indent:-1.5pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Former Executive Vice President and Worldwide Chairman, Consumer&nbsp;&nbsp;Johnson&#160;&amp; Johnson</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since: <font style="font-weight:normal;">May 2012</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Age:<font style="font-weight:normal;"> 57</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Independent</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committees:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;Audit</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.25pt;;text-indent:-7.5pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="font-family:Arial;">&#160;&#160;Governance, Membership and Public&#160;Affairs</font></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249395"></a>&nbsp;</p></td>

<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Mr.&#160;Mesquita was Executive Vice President and Worldwide Chairman, Consumer of Johnson&#160;&amp; Johnson (&#8220;J&amp;J&#8221;), a global healthcare products company, from December 2014 until February 2019. He served on J&amp;J&#8217;s Executive Committee and led the Consumer Group Operating Committee.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Prior to that, he was employed by P&amp;G, a global marketer of consumer products, in various marketing and leadership capacities for 29 years from 1984 to 2013. During his tenure at P&amp;G, he served as Group President&#160;&#8211;&#160;New Business Creation and Innovation from March 2012 until June 2013, Group President&#160;&#8211; Special Assignment from January 2012 until March 2012, Group President, Global Fabric Care from 2007 to 2011 and President, Global Home Care from 2001 to 2007, also serving as President of Commercial Products and President of P&amp;G Professional from 2006 to 2007.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:8.05pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:8.05pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Mesquita brings extensive experience leading major global company business units. In these roles, he has a strong track record of building and marketing global brands, including the reinvention of key brands, leading strategic business transformations and driving strong, profitable growth.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;As P&amp;G&#8217;s Group President, New Business Creation and Innovation, Mr.&#160;Mesquita redesigned the company&#8217;s business development organization and worked across the company with technology, marketing and finance leaders to develop groundbreaking innovation capabilities.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;He is known for driving innovation and has led large, complex supply chain organizations.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Mesquita was born and raised in Mozambique, Africa and is of Portuguese descent. He has lived and worked in several countries, including Venezuela, Mexico, Brazil and the United States. He is fluent in Portuguese, Spanish and English.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Mesquita has</font><font style="color:#5A2D82;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;">public company board and corporate governance experience, serving on the Board since 2012.</font></p></td>

<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249417"></a>Mr.&#160;Neubauer was Chairman of the Board of ARAMARK Corporation (&#8220;ARAMARK&#8221;), a leading provider of professional services including food, hospitality, facility and uniform services, from 1984 until his retirement in 2015.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Mr.&#160;Neubauer joined ARAMARK in 1979 as Executive Vice President of Finance and Development, Chief Financial Officer and a member of the Board of Directors. He was elected President in 1981, Chief Executive Officer in 1983 and Chairman in 1984. He served as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer until May 2012.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;As a former Chairman and Chief Executive of ARAMARK, Mr.&#160;Neubauer brings a wealth of experience in operational excellence in a complex international professional services organization. During Mr.&#160;Neubauer&#8217;s tenure at ARAMARK, revenues grew from $2&#160;billion to $14&#160;billion and operations extended into 21 countries.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Neubauer brings significant industry knowledge acquired during his career at ARAMARK and, before that, at PepsiCo.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Neubauer gained significant financial experience while serving as ARAMARK&#8217;s Chief Financial Officer and prior to joining ARAMARK in 1979, during his employment with The Chase Manhattan Bank and service as Treasurer of PepsiCo.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Neubauer</font><font style="color:#5A2D82;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;">has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. He is a former director of ARAMARK, Macy&#8217;s Inc. and Verizon Communications, Inc. and has served as Lead Director for the Mondel&#275;z International Board since 2018.</font></p></td>
</tr>
</table></div></div></div>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;ITEM 1. Election of Directors&#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<div style="width:100%;">
<div style="float:left;width:49%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU25"></a><font style="font-size:1pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</font></p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:15%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000064.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:88px;height:128px;"></p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">FREDRIC G. REYNOLDS</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Former Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, CBS Corporation</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director since:<font style="font-weight:normal;"> December 2007</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Age:<font style="font-weight:normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;68</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Independent</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:5.75pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Board Committees:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Audit (Chair)</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:17.75pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Finance</font></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:1pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk2249444"></a>Mr.&#160;Reynolds served as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of CBS Corporation (&#8220;CBS&#8221;), a mass media company, from 2006 until his retirement in 2009. From 2001 through 2005, Mr.&#160;Reynolds served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Viacom Television Stations Group, a mass media company, and as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of Viacom Inc. (&#8220;Viacom&#8221;), a mass media company, from 2000 to 2001. He also served as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of CBS and its predecessor, Westinghouse Electric Corporation, from 1994 to 2000.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.56%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Prior to that, Mr.&#160;Reynolds served in various capacities at PepsiCo for 12 years, including Chief Financial Officer or Financial Officer at food and beverage companies Pizza Hut, Pepsi Cola International, Kentucky Fried Chicken Worldwide and Frito-Lay.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E6E1EE" style="width:71%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Director Qualifications:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Reynolds has extensive experience in both the media (including advertising and marketing) and the food and beverage industries. He served in various executive roles at CBS, Viacom and PepsiCo. While at CBS, he successfully managed the integration following the CBS/Viacom merger, and he was ultimately responsible for all financial functions and growing the business portfolio at Viacom. During his tenure as Chief Financial Officer of CBS, CBS shareholders experienced substantial share appreciation and return of capital.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Reynolds brings extensive financial experience gained during his service as Chief Financial Officer at CBS and Viacom and at divisions of PepsiCo.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:6pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Reynolds is a Certified Public Accountant.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:18pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;Mr.&#160;Reynolds has extensive public company board and corporate governance experience. He is a director of Hess Corporation (until June 5, 2019) and United Technologies Corporation. He is a former director of AOL, Inc.</font></p></td>
</tr>
