<tr>
<td valign="middle"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:94%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:2.96%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:16pt;font-family:Calibri;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000013.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:85px;height:20px;"></p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:4pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:6%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">39</a></p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;Compensation Discussion and Analysis&#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:12pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU50"></a><a name="N2018_SAYONPAY_VOTE_SHAREHOLDER_OUTREACH"></a><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="N2018_SAYONPAY_VOTE_SHAREHOLDER_OUTREACH"></a>2018 Say-On-Pay Vote an</font><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">d Shareholder Outreach</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:1pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Weighting Organic net revenue growth-2.1% (below threshold) adjusted ROIC- 9.7% annualized relative TSR- 64th percentile 0% rating 80% rating 128% rating 84% Performance rating Below Threshold-0% Target-100% Maximum-200% <font style="color:#000000;"><br /></font>Weighting 40% 40% 10% 10% Organic net revenue growth- 0.9% 78% defined EPS&#8212;$2.03 good defined free cash flow-$1,579 million 68% cash conversion cycle -11 days 150% below threshold -0% target-100% maximum-200% 107% preliminary corporate rating-15 percentage point (&#8220;PP&#8221;) reduction for market share overlay 92% final corporate rating </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">We were very disappointed when only 45% of the votes cast at our 2018 annual meeting were in favor of our say-on-pay proposal. Historically, we have received an average of 90% of votes in favor of say-on-pay. Given the low 2018 vote, the Board and Compensation Committee recognized the vote reflected significant shareholder dissatisfaction. Therefore, we refocused our extensive shareholder outreach to better understand the reasons for the substantial decrease in support. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:18pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Significant Outreach to Shareholders</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">In response to the vote, we increased our dialogue with shareholders to obtain a thorough understanding of their concerns, their views on our overall executive compensation program and actions needed to address such concerns. Accordingly, in 2018 and 2019, non-employee directors and members of senior management conducted comprehensive shareholder engagement, including outreach to shareholders in the aggregate representing approximately 55% of our outstanding stock.&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:18pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">What We Heard and How We Are Responding</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Throughout our discussions, we heard broad support for our ongoing compensation programs, but shareholders consistently raised concerns relating to the compensation actions supporting the CEO succession and transition in 2017. Although these were one-off actions taken in response to a particular situation and not part of our regular executive compensation program, we have taken the feedback into consideration and will continue to do so when structuring compensation in similar circumstances in the future. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The chart below details the concerns we heard from shareholders and how we are responding to those concerns:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:102.1%;">
<tr>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:51.42%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">SHAREHOLDER CONCERNS</p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:48.58%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">HOW WE ARE RESPONDING</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#F2F2F2" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:51.42%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Substantial make-whole awards for our new CEO, a </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">small proportion of which was considered to be performance</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">based</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#F2F2F2" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:48.58%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The Committee understands shareholder concerns around non-performance based recruitment packages and will endeavor to emphasize performance-based recruitment compensation going forward.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:28.5pt;">
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#F2F2F2" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:51.42%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Time-based retention grants to two NEOs</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#F2F2F2" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:48.58%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The Committee uses retention grants only in exceptional circumstances. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">No retention grants were made in 2018.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The retention grant made to Brian Gladden in 2017 was fully forfeited upon his separation in July 2018. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Should the Committee determine that retention grants are necessary in the future, it will consider performance-based vesting conditions to the extent practical and applicable. </p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#F2F2F2" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:51.42%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Waiving prorata vesting treatment for the retiring CEO&#8217;s</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">outstanding performance share units</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#F2F2F2" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:48.58%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:13.55pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">No other retiring NEO has received special vesting treatment nor do we intend to make any further exceptions to equity treatment in connection with future retirements. </p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:bold;;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:94%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>

<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-Right:4pt;width:6%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">40</a></p></td>
<td valign="middle"  style="width:94%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:16pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#5A2D82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2019 Proxy Statement</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;Compensation Discussion and Analysis&#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU51"></a><a name="HOW_WE_DESIGN_OUR_EXECUTIVE_COMPENSATION"></a><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="HOW_WE_DESIGN_OUR_EXECUTIVE_COMPENSATION"></a>How We Design our Executi</font><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">ve Compensation </font><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Program</font><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"> </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The Compensation Committee oversees our executive compensation program focusing on the following primary goals: </p>
<div align="left">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"  style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top" style="width:7.94%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top" style="width:3.4%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">1.</font></p></td>
<td valign="top">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">Attract, retain and motivate talented executives and develop world-class business leaders; </p></td></tr></table></div>
<div align="left">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"  style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top" style="width:7.94%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top" style="width:3.4%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2.</font></p></td>
<td valign="top">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">Support business strategies that promote superior long-term shareholder returns; </p></td></tr></table></div>
<div align="left">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"  style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top" style="width:7.94%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top" style="width:3.4%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">3.</font></p></td>
<td valign="top">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">Align pay and performance by making a significant portion of our executives&#8217; compensation dependent on achieving financial and other critical strategic and individual goals; and </p></td></tr></table></div>
<div align="left">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"  style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top" style="width:7.94%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top" style="width:3.4%;white-space:nowrap">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">4.</font></p></td>
<td valign="top">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;">Align our executives&#8217; and shareholders&#8217; interests through equity-based incentive grants that link executive compensation to sustained and superior TSR and stock ownership requirements. </p></td></tr></table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:18pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Design Principles:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:33.34%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:-0.35pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;What we do:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:33.34%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:12.95pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">How we do it:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="width:33.32%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:12.95pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Our objective:</p></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:3.75pt;">
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="padding-left:8pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:33.34%; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="width:33.34%; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="width:33.32%; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:3pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="padding-left:8pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:33.34%; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:4pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003; <font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Link pay to performance and put pay at risk</font><font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">. </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003;<font style="font-family:Arial;"> </font><font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;">Use a mix of equity and cash incentives. </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003;<font style="font-family:Arial;"> </font><font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;">Compensate based on financial performance of the business while also considering individual performance. </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003;<font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;"> </font><font style="font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Target compensation at or near the median of our Compensation Survey Peer Group. We compensate fairly and competitively.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003;<font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;"> </font><font style="font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Set substantive performance goals at the beginning of performance cycles and hold executives accountable for delivering on those targets.</font><font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;"> </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003;<font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;"> </font><font style="font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Reward long-term sustainable performance.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-10pt;;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Segoe UI Symbol;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#10003;<font style="font-style:italic;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;"> </font><font style="font-style:italic;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Reinforce stock ownership requirements.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9.5pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:33.34%; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:4pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 88% <font style="font-weight:normal;">of our CEO&#8217;s compensation</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; and <font style="font-weight:bold;">78%</font> of other NEO</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; compensation is at-risk.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <font style="font-weight:bold;">71% </font>of our CEO&#8217;s compensation</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; and <font style="font-weight:bold;">58%</font> of other NEO</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; compensation is in equity based</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; grants based on long-term</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; performance.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:9pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; The CEO&#8217;s annual target pay package is <font style="font-weight:bold;">85% </font>of the median of our 2018 compensation peers.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:bold;;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; Performance goals reflect</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; challenging annual and long-term</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; objectives designed to accomplish</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; our business strategy. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; Executives must hold the net shares</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; (shares remaining after the payment</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; of taxes and any exercise price)</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; received upon the exercise of stock</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; options or vesting of deferred stock</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; units or performance share units</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; until the stock ownership guideline</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; is met; in addition, <font style="font-weight:bold;">all net shares</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;must be held at least one year</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;from exercise/vesting regardless</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;of ownership compliance. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;line-height:11pt;margin-left:13pt;;margin-right:0.74%;text-indent:-13pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="width:33.32%; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:4pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Heavily weight the mix of fixed and variable compensation toward the variable components to align compensation with achieving relevant financial, strategic and individual performance goals.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Heavily weight the mix of incentives toward equity that vests over multiple years to focus executives on achieving long-term TSR that exceeds the peer median and aligns with the interests of our shareholders.<font style="font-size:4pt;"> </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Design targets to advance our long-term business strategy without incentivizing excessive risk-taking.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:6pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Require our executives to hold specified levels of stock to align their interests with shareholders and discourage short-term decision-making over driving long-term performance.</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<td valign="top"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:6%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="middle"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:94%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:2.96%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:16pt;font-family:Calibri;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000013.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:85px;height:20px;"></p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:4pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:6%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">41</a></p></td>
</tr>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;Compensation Discussion and Analysis&#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:12pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU52"></a><a name="CHANGES_TO_OUR_EXECUTIVE_COMPENSATION_PR"></a><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="CHANGES_TO_OUR_EXECUTIVE_COMPENSATION_PR"></a>Changes to our Executiv</font><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5A2D82;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">e Compensation Program</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Although concerns expressed by shareholders were primarily related to one-time events in 2017 and not our ongoing executive compensation program, we did make some changes to our executive compensation program in both 2018 and 2019 to enhance our pay-for-performance culture and support our new strategy; these changes were generally well received during discussions with shareholders.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td colspan="4" valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#5B2B82" style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:100%; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Annual Incentive Program Changes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:19.8pt;">
<td valign="middle"  style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:25%; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:-3.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2018</p></td>
<td valign="middle"  style="width:25%; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-right:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Program Design</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_Hlk3964064"></a>&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;<font style="font-family:Arial;color:#000000;">Increased weighting of <br />financial results to 80% <br /><a name="_Hlk3964064"></a>(from 60% previously) and reduced individual <br />performance weighting <br />to 20% (from 40% </font></p>
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">previously).</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Fully aligned all commercial <br />leaders to local operational <br />results. </p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-right:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Better align annual cash incentive </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">awards to objective, quantifiable </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">financial performance goals. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-4.5pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Incent commercial leaders to </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">deliver strong results in local </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">markets.</p>
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;No additional changes to </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">program design.</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">

<tr style="height:19.75pt;">
<td colspan="4" valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#E5E5E5" style="width:100%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;Performance Measures</p></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:31.95pt;">
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Added Adjusted Gross Margin Percent, weighted at 20% of <br />the financial performance rating.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Removed cash conversion <br />cycle. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Removed market share overlay.</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Align to the last year of the </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">margin expansion goal and </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">promote growth and long-term </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">brand health.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Achieved the desired impact of </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">changing the culture to reduce </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">cash conversion volatility during </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">the year.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Focus executives only on key metrics committed to in 2018 (i.e. Free Cash Flow and margin expansion). </p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Added Organic Volume as a </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">metric weighted at 15% of</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">the financial performance </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">rating.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Reduced weighting of </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Organic Net Revenue </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Growth to 25%.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Replaced Adjusted Gross </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Margin Percent with </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Adjusted Gross Profit </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">dollars (with a 20% </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">weighting).</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Added market share overlay.</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:25%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Balance top-line growth </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">metrics; focus on volume and </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">revenue metrics is healthy for </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">the business and produces </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">higher quality and more </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">sustainable earnings.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Adjusted Gross Profit dollars </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">supports the new strategy of </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">focusing on growing both local </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">and global brands.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Market share enables us to </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">assess and incent quality of </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">results, an important aspect of </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:22.5pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">the new strategy.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:9pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>

</tr>
<tr style="height:31.95pt;">
<td valign="top"  style="width:32%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #683F8B;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:13.05pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Replaced Adjusted Return on Invested Capital (&#8220;ROIC&#8221;) Increase with Adjusted <br />EPS growth. </p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:36%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:20.6pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Over the past three years we made strong progress in improving Adjusted ROIC from 7.5% to 10%.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:8pt;margin-left:20.6pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;However, our balance sheet is predominantly Goodwill which restricts our ability to further impact ROIC.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:8pt;margin-left:20.6pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;We are shifting to an Adjusted EPS growth metric since increased profitability is the key lever for further impacting ROIC; provides clear line of sight and aligns with shareholder interests.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:40.05pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:32%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #683F8B; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;No change from 2018.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:-9pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="top"  style="width:6%;">
<p style="margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:94%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-Right:4pt;width:6%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">42</a></p></td>
<td valign="middle"  style="width:94%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:16pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#5A2D82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2019 Proxy Statement</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;Compensation Discussion and Analysis&#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td style="width:540pt;"></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:20.25pt;">
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B">
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Peer Group Changes for 2019</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The Company uses two different groups of companies to benchmark executive compensation and assess relative performance. We use our Compensation Survey Peer Group to assess the competitiveness of the compensation of our named executive officers (global peers of similar size who are primarily consumer-facing). We use our Performance Peer Group to assess relative performance (industry peers).</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">The Compensation Committee, with input from its independent compensation consultant, refreshed our Compensation Survey Peer Group in 2019. We had not changed this peer group since 2012 and changes in the Company warranted a review of our comparator companies. Reassessing this peer group resulted in a set of compensation peers more closely aligned to our business, complexity, breadth, scope, median revenues and market capitalization. The median revenue of our new Compensation Survey Peer Group is $25.3 billion compared to our 2018 revenue of $25.9 billion. We made the following changes to the Compensation Survey Peer Group for 2019:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:12pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<div align="left">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;  margin-left:12.43%;width:52.67%;">
<tr>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:53.84%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">ADDED</p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:46.16%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">REMOVED</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:53.84%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 1pt #7030A0; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;white-space:nowrap;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;margin-right:1.67%;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;The Est&#233;e Lauder Companies Inc.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;margin-right:1.67%;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Newell Brands Inc.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;margin-right:1.67%;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Starbucks Corporation</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:2pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:46.16%; border-top:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-bottom:solid 1pt #7030A0; border-left:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82; border-right:solid 0.75pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Abbott Laboratories</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Danone<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top"> </sup>&#160; </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;DowDuPont Inc.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Nestl&#233; S.A.<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top"> </sup>&#160; </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Pfizer Inc.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;Unilever PLC<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:3pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:30pt;;text-indent:-18pt;;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;United Parcel Service, Inc.</p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
