<tr>
<td valign="bottom"  style="width:20%; border-bottom:solid 1.5pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;line-height:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU102"></a><font style="font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Measures</font></p></td>
<td valign="bottom"  style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:33%; border-bottom:solid 1.5pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="line-height:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Definitions</p>
<p style="line-height:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(Including&#160;Adjustment to&#160;GAAP&#160;Measure)</p></td>
<td valign="bottom"  style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:27%; border-bottom:solid 1.5pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="line-height:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Modifications</p></td>
<td valign="bottom"  style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:20%; border-bottom:solid 1.5pt #5B2B82;">
<p style="line-height:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Rationale</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  style="width:20%;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Defined EPS</p>
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(Annual Cash Incentive&#160;Program)</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:33%;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Adjusted EPS is defined as diluted EPS attributable to Mondel&#275;z International from continuing operations excluding the impacts&#160;of:</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;the Simplify to Grow Program</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(</sup><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">3</sup><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;">;</font></p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;gains or losses (including non-cash impairment charges) on goodwill and intangible assets;</font></p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;divestiture<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup></font> or acquisition gains or losses&#160;and related divestiture<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup>, acquisition and integration costs;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;net earnings from divestitures<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;remeasurement of net monetary position<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(4)</sup>;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;mark-to-market impacts from commodity and forecasted currency transaction derivative contracts<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(5</sup><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;impact from resolution of tax matters<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(6)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;CEO transition remuneration<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(7)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;impact from pension participation changes<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(8)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;incremental expenses related to the 2017 malware incident;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;losses on debt extinguishment and related&#160;expenses;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;gain on equity method investment transactions;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;gains or losses on interest swaps no longer designated as accounting cash flow hedges due to changed financing and hedging plans;<font style="font-size:3pt;">&#160;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;U.S. tax reform discrete impacts<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(9)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">And within Adjusted EPS:</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.2pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;equity method investment earnings exclude our proportionate share of our investees&#8217;&#160;unusual or infrequent items<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(10)</sup></font>.</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:19.45pt;;text-indent:-12.25pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:27%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Defined EPS<font style="font-style:normal;">: Defined as Adjusted EPS calculated at currency exchange rates utilized in our internal financial planning for 2018.</font></p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="width:20%;">
<p style="margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:7.2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Indicator of overall business trends and performance, based on what business leaders can control.</p></td>

<td valign="middle"  style="width:94%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:16pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;color:#5A2D82;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2019 Proxy Statement</p></td>

<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;Financial Measures Definitions &#160;&#160;</font></p>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td valign="bottom"  style="width:25.84%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Measures</p></td>
<td colspan="2" valign="bottom"  style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:47.58%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Definitions</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(Including&#160;Adjustment to&#160;GAAP&#160;Measure)</p></td>
<td valign="bottom"  style="padding-left:7.2pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:26.58%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#5B2B82;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Rationale</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:25.84%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Free Cash Flow </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(Annual&#160;Cash Incentive Program)</p></td>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:47.58%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Free Cash Flow is defined as Net Cash Provided By Operating Activities less capital expenditures.</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#EEE9F2" style="width:auto;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Reflects financial liquidity,</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">working capital efficiency</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">and financial health.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" style="width:25.84%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Adjusted ROIC </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(Performance&#160;Share Units)</p></td>
<td colspan="2" valign="bottom"  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" style="width:47.58%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Adjusted Net Operating Profit After Taxes (&#8220;NOPAT&#8221;) divided by Adjusted Invested Capital, which are defined below:</p></td>
<td rowspan="2" valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" style="width:auto;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:2pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Reflects a metric used to measure effectiveness in managing working capital and stresses the importance of continued focus on asset and cash management.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" style="width:25.84%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:8pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" style="width:25.8%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Adjusted NOPAT is defined as Operating&#160;Income less taxes plus Equity&#160;Method Investment Earnings&#160;excluding the&#160;impacts&#160;of:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;the Simplify to Grow Program</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(3)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;">;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;divestiture</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;"> or acquisition gains or&#160;losses and related divestiture<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup>, acquisition and integration costs;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;gains or losses (including non-cash&#160;impairment charges) on&#160;goodwill and&#160;intangible assets;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;the operating results of divestitures</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(1)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;">;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;remeasurement of net monetary position<sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(4)</sup>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;mark-to-market impacts from commodity and forecasted currency transaction derivative<br />contracts<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(5)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Impact from the resolution of tax matters<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(6)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;CEO transition remuneration<font style="font-size:7pt;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(7)</sup></font>;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;impact form pension participation changers</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(8)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;">;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.25pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12.25pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;incremental expenses related to the 2017 malware incident;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12.25pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12.25pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;gain on equity method investment transactions;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;U.S. tax reform discrete impacts</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(9)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;">;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">And Equity Method Investment Earnings&#160;excludes<font style="font-style:italic;">:</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:3pt;margin-left:12pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;our proportionate share of&#160;our&#160;investees&#8217; unusual or&#160;infrequent items</font><font style="font-size:7pt;color:#000000;"><sup style="font-size:85%; vertical-align:top">(10)</sup></font><font style="color:#000000;">.</font></p></td>
<td valign="top"  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" style="width:auto;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:2pt;margin-left:3pt;;margin-right:0.69%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Adjusted Invested Capital (calculated as the simple average of beginning and year-end balances) is&#160;defined as:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Current assets, excluding cash;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Property, Plant and Equipment,&#160;net;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Goodwill;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Intangibles, net; and</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Other Assets adjusted for&#160;the&#160;JDE investment step-up&#160;recorded in 2015.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:3pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-style:italic;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Less:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Current liabilities, excluding Debt;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Deferred Taxes;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Accrued Pension and Postretirement;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Other Liabilities; and</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;font-size:3pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:1pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:15pt;;text-indent:-12pt;;color:#4C4C4C;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#8226;<font style="color:#000000;">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Non-Controlling Interest.</font></p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<tr>
<td valign="top"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:94%;">
<p style="margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:6%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="middle"  style="padding-left:0pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:94%;">
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:0pt;;margin-right:2.22%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:16pt;font-family:Calibri;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000013.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:85px;height:20px;"></p></td>
<td valign="middle"  BGCOLOR="#683F8B" style="padding-left:4pt;padding-Right:0pt;padding-Top:0pt;padding-Bottom:0pt;width:6%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">A-3</a></p></td>
</tr>
</table></div>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2D83;">&#160;&#160;Financial Measures Definitions &#160;&#160;</font></p>
<p style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(1) Divestitures include completed sales of businesses and the exits of major product lines upon completion of a sale or licensing agreement. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(2) Constant currency operating results are calculated by dividing or multiplying, as appropriate, the current-period local currency operating results by the currency exchange rates used to translate the financial statements in the comparable prior-year period to determine what the current-period U.S. dollar operating results would have been if the currency exchange rate had not changed from the comparable prior-year period. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(3) Non-GAAP adjustments related to the Simplify to Grow Program reflect costs incurred that relate to the objectives of our program to transform our supply chain network and organizational structure. Costs that do not meet the program objectives are not reflected in the non-GAAP adjustments. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(4) During the third quarter of 2018, as we began to apply highly inflationary accounting for Argentina, we excluded the remeasurement gains or losses related to remeasuring net monetary assets or liabilities in Argentina to be consistent with our prior accounting for these remeasurement gains or losses for Venezuela when it was subject to highly inflationary accounting prior to 2016. See Note 1, <font style="font-style:italic;">Summary of Significant Accounting Policies, </font>in our 2018 Form 10-K for more information<font style="font-style:italic;">.</font> </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(5) During the third quarter of 2016, we began to exclude unrealized gains and losses (mark-to-market impacts) from outstanding commodity and forecasted currency transaction derivatives from our non-GAAP earnings measures until such time that the related exposures impact our operating results. Since we purchase commodity and forecasted currency transaction contracts to mitigate price volatility primarily for inventory requirements in future periods, we made this adjustment to remove the volatility of these future inventory purchases on current operating results to facilitate comparisons of our underlying operating performance across periods. We also discontinued designating commodity and forecasted currency transaction derivatives for hedge accounting treatment. To facilitate comparisons of our underlying operating results, we have recast all historical non-GAAP earnings measures to exclude the mark-to-market impacts. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(6) See Note 13, <font style="font-style:italic;">Commitments and Contingencies &#8211; Tax Matters</font>, in our 2018 Form 10-K for more information. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(7) On November&#160;20, 2017 Dirk Van de Put succeeded Irene Rosenfeld as CEO of Mondel&#275;z International in advance of her retirement at the end of March 2018. In order to incent Mr.&#160;Van de Put to join us, we provided him compensation with a total combined target value of $42.5&#160;million to make him whole for incentive awards he forfeited or grants that were not made to him when he left his former employer. The compensation we granted took the form of cash, deferred stock units, performance share units and stock options. In connection with Irene Rosenfeld&#8217;s retirement, we made her outstanding grants of performance share units for the 2016-2018 and 2017-2019 performance cycles eligible for continued vesting and approved a $0.5&#160;million salary for her service as Chairman from January through March 2018. We refer to these elements of Mr.&#160;Van de Put&#8217;s and Ms.&#160;Rosenfeld&#8217;s compensation arrangements together as &#8220;CEO transition remuneration.&#8221; We are excluding amounts we expense as CEO transition remuneration from our non-GAAP results because those amounts are not part of our regular compensation program and are incremental to amounts we would have incurred as ongoing CEO compensation. As a result, in 2017, we excluded amounts expensed for the cash payment to Mr.&#160;Van de Put and partial vesting of his equity grants. In 2018, we excluded amounts paid for Ms.&#160;Rosenfeld&#8217;s service as Chairman and partial vesting of Mr.&#160;Van de Put&#8217;s and Ms.&#160;Rosenfeld&#8217;s equity grants. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(8) The impact from pension participation changes represents the charges incurred when employee groups are withdrawn from multiemployer pension plans and other changes in employee group pension plan participation. We exclude these charges from our non&#8211;GAAP results because those amounts do not reflect our ongoing pension obligations. See Note 10, <font style="font-style:italic;">Benefit Plans</font>, in our 2018 Form 10-K for more information. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(9) On December&#160;22, 2017, the United States enacted tax reform legislation that included a broad range of business tax provisions as further detailed in Note 15, <font style="font-style:italic;">Income Taxes</font>, in our 2018 Form 10-K. We exclude the discrete U.S. tax reform impacts from our Adjusted EPS as they do not reflect our ongoing tax obligations under U.S. tax reform. </p>
<p style="margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:8pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">(10) We have excluded our proportionate share of our equity method investees&#8217; unusual or infrequent items such as acquisition and divestiture related costs, restructuring program costs and discrete U.S. tax reform impacts, in order to provide investors with a comparable view of our performance across periods. Although we have shareholder rights and board representation commensurate with our ownership interests in our equity method investees and review the underlying operating results and unusual or infrequent items with them each reporting period, we do not have direct control over their operations or resulting revenue and expenses. Our use of equity method investment net earnings on an adjusted basis is not intended to imply that we have any such control. Our GAAP &#8220;diluted EPS attributable to Mondel&#275;z International from continuing operations&#8221; includes all of the investees&#8217; unusual and infrequent items. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2.55%;text-indent:-2.55%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:2pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:2.55%;text-indent:-2.55%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:2pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<div>

<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="_AEIOULastRenderedPageBreakAEIOU106"></a><font style="font-size:1pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;color:#5A2D82;font-size:16pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><a name="toc498940_61"></a><a name="MAPS_DIRECTIONS"></a><a name="MAPS_DIRECTIONS"></a>Map and Directions </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">2019 Annual Meeting of Shareholders </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">May&#160;15, 2019 <font style="color:#5A2D82;">&#8226;</font> 9:00 a.m. CDT </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">NOAH&#8217;S Event Venue </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">200 Barclay Boulevard </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Lincolnshire, Illinois 60069 </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:12pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000142.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:651px;height:423px;"></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:12pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">Directions to NOAH&#8217;S Event Venue </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant: normal;">Noah&#8217;s <font style="text-transform:none;">is located in the Lincolnshire Corporate Center directly off of Half Day Road in Lincolnshire, Illinois. </font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">From Northbound Milwaukee Avenue, turn left onto Half Day Road, and then turn left onto Barclay Boulevard. Barclay Boulevard is approximately 0.2 miles west of Milwaukee Avenue. <font style="text-transform:uppercase;">Noah&#8217;s</font> will be the second building on the west side of Barclay Boulevard, just south of Staybridge Suites. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">From Southbound Milwaukee Avenue, turn right onto Half Day Road, then turn left onto Barclay Boulevard. Barclay Boulevard is approximately 0.2 miles west of Milwaukee Avenue. <font style="text-transform:uppercase;">Noah&#8217;s</font> will be the second building on the west side of Barclay Boulevard, just south of Staybridge Suites. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:6pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">From the Tri-State Tollway (Route I-294) which becomes Route I-94, exit at IL-22/Half Day Road. Go west on IL-22/Half Day Road approximately 2.6 miles. Turn left onto Barclay Boulevard. <font style="text-transform:uppercase;">Noah&#8217;s</font> will be the second building on the west side of Barclay Boulevard, just south of Staybridge Suites. </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:12pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000143.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:172px;height:78px;"></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-weight:bold;color:#FCFCFC;font-size:1pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><font style="Background-color:#5B2B82;">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:1pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="page-break-after:always;width:100%;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:6pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:0%;font-size:12pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;"><img src="gycirsmwh4vw000144.jpg" title="" alt="" style="width:719px;height:919px;"></p>

<td colspan="5" valign="top"  style=" border-left:solid 2.25pt #000000; border-right:solid 2.25pt #000000;">
<p style="margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-left:11.6pt;;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#231F20;font-size:8pt;font-family:Calibri;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">This<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt;">pr</font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt;">oxy</font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>is<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>solicited<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>by<font style="letter-spacing:-0.8pt;"> </font>the<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.05pt;">Boar</font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt;">d</font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>of<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.1pt;">Directors</font><font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>for<font style="letter-spacing:-0.8pt;"> </font>use<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>at<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>the<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>Annual<font style="letter-spacing:-0.8pt;"> </font>Meeting<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>on<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>May<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>15,<font style="letter-spacing:-0.85pt;"> </font>2019.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:4pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:11.6pt;;margin-right:4.44%;text-indent:0pt;;font-size:8pt;font-family:Calibri;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">By signing the proxy, you revoke all prior proxies and appoint Jeffrey S. Srulovitz and Jenny L. Lauth and each or either of them with full power of substitution, to vote shares on the matters shown on the reverse side of this card and any other matters which may come before the Annual Meeting or any postponements or adjournments thereof (including, if applicable, any matter which the Board of Directors did not know would be presented at the Annual Meeting of Shareholders by a reasonable time before the proxy solicitation was made or for the election of a person to the Board of Directors if any nominee named in Proposal 1 becomes unable to serve or for good cause will not serve).</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:4pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:10pt;;margin-right:4.44%;text-indent:0pt;;font-weight:bold;color:#231F20;font-size:8pt;font-family:Calibri;letter-spacing:-0.3pt;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant: normal;">THIS PROXY, WHEN PROPERLY EXECUTED, WILL BE VOTED IN THE MANNER DESIGNATED ON THE REVERSE SIDE. IF NO OTHER INDICATION IS MADE ON THE REVERSE SIDE OF THIS FORM, THE PROXIES WILL VOTE "FOR" EACH OF THE DIRECTOR NOMINEES LISTED IN PROPOSAL 1, "FOR" PROPOSALS 2 AND 3, "AGAINST" PROPOSALS 4 AND 5 AND IN THEIR DISCRETION UPON SUCH OTHER BUSINESS AS PROPERLY COMES BEFORE THE MEETING OR ANY POSTPONEMENT OR ADJOURNMENT THEREOF.</p>
